{"tid":1140752,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"傳利物浦為爭首個英超錦標設下暗花","createTime":"2019-05-06T04:54:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-18T11:43:12.000Z","uid":251052,"like":138,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"5b03f83e733dbf00029ae6f710d30942dd082ff4","tid":1140752,"uid":251052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T04:54:54.000Z","msg":"（綜合英格蘭外電）利物浦為了爭奪首個英超冠軍而出動「暗花」戰術？<br />\n據消息人士透露，利物浦為白禮頓球員設下暗花，只要在最後一輪英超比賽中勝出或逼和曼城，利物浦將會為他們提供每人200萬英鎊獎金。<br />\n<br />\n然而曼城方面如果成功衞冕英超，曼城陣中最「和味」的是阿古路，可獲三百萬歐羅，而史達寧則獲二百七十五萬歐羅，其他正選則獲二百六十五萬歐羅，連後備球員也可獲三十萬歐羅，因此即使以金錢掛帥角度，曼城的戰意仍然遠勝白禮頓。"},{"pid":"0cf27382c30fa8fdc74201e86d5ff67892c988cf","tid":1140752,"uid":81273,"like":120,"dislike":1,"score":119,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T04:55:57.000Z","msg":"曼城出夠一千萬呀"},{"pid":"85c8b1c2816c8e90df3e65bbfd8456a1ed94324c","tid":1140752,"uid":3747,"like":140,"dislike":1,"score":139,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T04:57:45.000Z","msg":"中間人傳錯話係阿記用哂d力啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eba0b4249381226401ee47f53531738b9477920","tid":1140752,"uid":173852,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85c8b1c2816c8e90df3e65bbfd8456a1ed94324c","tid":1140752,"uid":3747,"like":140,"dislike":1,"score":139,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T04:57:45.000Z","msg":"中間人傳錯話係阿記用哂d力啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T05:03:34.000Z","msg":"可能唔止利記落呢 白禮頓收足幾家茶禮<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"837c750759b91ff595c5ad03ed9624fbf67ef0c0","tid":1140752,"uid":42820,"like":72,"dislike":4,"score":68,"quote":{"pid":"0cf27382c30fa8fdc74201e86d5ff67892c988cf","tid":1140752,"uid":81273,"like":120,"dislike":1,"score":119,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T04:55:57.000Z","msg":"曼城出夠一千萬呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-